  "text": "Knowing what you know now about our planetary condition and evidence of communication, etc. If you, yourself as an individual, had gone through the process of incarnation here as a wanderer, and now have memory of a sufficient way to have the objective that you just stated. What mechanisms would you seek out for the process of teach learning in our present state of communication? I am Ra, my brother. We perceive you have made certain unspoken connections. We acknowledge these and for this reason cannot infringe upon your confusion.",
